### About 
- Dynamite SDKs: `1.0 (beta)`
- Kibana Package Manager: `0.1`                                                                                   |

### Core Dependencies
- Zeek `3.0.3` [[BSD](https://github.com/zeek/zeek/blob/master/COPYING)]

- Filebeat-OSS `7.11.1` [[Apache 2](https://github.com/elastic/beats/blob/7.12/licenses/APACHE-LICENSE-2.0.txt )]
- OpenSearch Stack `7.11.1` [[Apache 2](https://aws.github.io/)]
